This simple Program is used to control your PC WiFi and Bluetooth devices

With WiFi Menu You Can:
-----------------------
1. Display WiFi Status
2. Turn WiFi On
3. Turn WiFi Off
4. Connect to WiFi Network
5. Remove a Saved Network
6. Modify a Saved Network
7. Search for a Network

With Bluetooth Menu You Can:
-----------------------
1. Display Bluetooth Status
2. Turn Bluetooth On
3. Turn Bluetooth Off
4. Connect to Bluetooth Device

-----------------------------------------------------------
To run the program just left click the APP.sh and run it as program.
there is an image "How To Execute Program" in this directory clarifies this.
-----------------------------------------------------------
